<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>HoldOff Pricing — Respect Yourself</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Choose the plan that fits your commitment to yourself. Simple pricing, no games.">
  
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F172A 0%, #1a1f3a 50%, #2d1b4e 100%);
      color: #e0e7ff;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
      max-width: 1400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .logo { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; color: #c4b5fd; }

    nav a {
      color: #cbd5e1;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 1.5rem;
      font-size: 14px;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }
    nav a:hover { color: #a78bfa; }

    .cta-btn {
      padding: 10px 24px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6, #6d28d9);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .cta-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
    }

    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px 2rem;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 48px;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a78bfa, #93c5fd);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #cbd5e1;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .pricing-container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 60px auto;
      padding: 0 2rem;
    }

    .pricing-intro {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .pricing-intro h2 {
      font-size: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #a78bfa;
    }

    .pricing-intro p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #cbd5e1;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    }

    .pricing-cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1400px) {
      .pricing-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .pricing-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .pricing-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero h1 { font-size: 32px; }
    }

    .pricing-card {
      background: rgba(100, 116, 139, 0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      position: relative;
    }

    .pricing-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.5);
      background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
      transform: translateY(-8px);
    }

    .pricing-card.popular {
      border-color: #8b5cf6;
      background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.15);
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    .pricing-card.popular:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05) translateY(-8px);
    }

    .badge {
      position: absolute;
      top: -12px;
      left: 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6, #6d28d9);
      color: white;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .plan-name {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: #a78bfa;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    .plan-desc {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #94a3b8;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .price {
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
      color: #a78bfa;
    }

    .price-period {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #cbd5e1;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .plan-features {
      list-style: none;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      flex-grow: 1;
    }

    .plan-features li {
      padding: 0.75rem 0;
      color: #cbd5e1;
      font-size: 14px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
    }

    .plan-features li:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .plan-features li:before {
      content: "✓ ";
      color: #10b981;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-right: 0.5rem;
    }

    .plan-cta {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6, #6d28d9);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }

    .plan-cta:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
    }

    .plan-cta.secondary {
      background: transparent;
      color: #a78bfa;
      border: 2px solid #a78bfa;
    }

    .plan-cta.secondary:hover {
      background: rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.1);
    }

    .faq-section {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 60px auto;
      padding: 0 2rem;
    }

    .faq-section h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      color: #a78bfa;
    }

    .faq-item {
      background: rgba(100, 116, 139, 0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .faq-item h3 {
      color: #a78bfa;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .faq-item p {
      color: #cbd5e1;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .disclaimer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-size: 12px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
      margin-top: 4rem;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      color: #64748b;
      font-size: 12px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1);
    }

    footer a {
      color: #a78bfa;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- HEADER -->
  <header>
    <div class="logo">HoldOff</div>
    <nav>
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="https://shouldiholdoff.live/login" style="color: #8b5cf6;">Sign In</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Respect Yourself</h1>
    <p>Simple pricing. No hidden fees. One goal: help you stop settling.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- PRICING CARDS -->
  <section class="pricing-container">
    <div class="pricing-intro">
      <h2>Choose Your Commitment</h2>
      <p>Every plan includes message analysis and AI verdicts. The difference is archive depth, coaching level, and support. Or lock in Lifetime and never think about it again.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="pricing-cards">
      <!-- FREE TRIAL PLAN -->
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <div class="plan-name">Trial</div>
        <div class="plan-desc">Test the pause. See if it helps.</div>
        <div class="price">Free</div>
        <div class="price-period">7 days</div>
        <ul class="plan-features">
          <li>Unlimited message analysis</li>
          <li>AI Verdict feedback</li>
          <li>Basic pattern tracking</li>
          <li>7-day message history</li>
          <li>Standard support</li>
        </ul>
        <button class="plan-cta secondary" onclick="window.location.href='https://shouldiholdoff.live/signup'">Start Free</button>
      </div>

      <!-- BASIC PLAN -->
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <div class="plan-name">Basic</div>
        <div class="plan-desc">Essential features at a fair price.</div>
        <div class="price">$9.99</div>
        <div class="price-period">per month</div>
        <ul class="plan-features">
          <li>Everything in Trial</li>
          <li>30-day message archive</li>
          <li>Pattern insights & trends</li>
          <li>Basic AI coaching</li>
          <li>Priority support</li>
          <li>Ad-free experience</li>
        </ul>
        <button class="plan-cta secondary" onclick="handlePricingCTA()">Choose Basic</button>
      </div>

      <!-- PREMIUM PLAN (POPULAR) - EARLY ADOPTER -->
      <div class="pricing-card popular">
        <div class="badge">Early Adopter</div>
        <div class="plan-name">Premium</div>
        <div class="plan-desc">The real commitment to yourself.</div>
        <div class="price">$4.99</div>
        <div class="price-period">per month <span style="font-size: 12px; color: #cbd5e1;">for 6 months</span></div>
        <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #10b981; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;"><strong>First 50 users only.</strong> Then $14.99/month.</div>
        <ul class="plan-features">
          <li>Everything in Basic</li>
          <li>90-day message archive</li>
          <li>Advanced pattern insights</li>
          <li>AI coaching responses</li>
          <li>VIP support</li>
          <li>Custom profiles</li>
        </ul>
        <button class="plan-cta" onclick="handlePricingCTA()">Get Early Adopter</button>
      </div>

      <!-- LIFETIME PLAN -->
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <div class="plan-name">Lifetime</div>
        <div class="plan-desc">One-time investment, forever freedom.</div>
        <div class="price">$199</div>
        <div class="price-period">one time</div>
        <ul class="plan-features">
          <li>Everything in Premium</li>
          <li>Unlimited message archive</li>
          <li>Advanced AI coaching</li>
          <li>Custom condition profiles</li>
          <li>Direct founder support</li>
          <li>Access to beta features</li>
        </ul>
        <button class="plan-cta" onclick="handlePricingCTA()">Go Lifetime</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="faq-section">
    <h2>Questions?</h2>
    
    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Can I upgrade or downgrade anytime?</h3>
      <p>Yes. You can upgrade to Lifetime from Plus at any time, and only pay the difference. No lock-in, no penalty.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>What if I don't like it?</h3>
      <p>We offer a 7-day money-back guarantee. If HoldOff doesn't help, we'll refund you, no questions asked.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Is my data private?</h3>
      <p>Absolutely. Your messages stay on your device. We never sell your data. Read our full privacy policy for details.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Do I need a subscription after my trial?</h3>
      <p>No. The Trial plan works forever. But if you want deeper insights and longer history, Plus or Lifetime unlock that.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>What's included in "AI Coaching"?</h3>
      <p>Beyond the Verdict (safe/risky), Plus and Lifetime plans get personalized coaching: why you want to send this, what pattern this triggers, and what respecting yourself looks like right now.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>What happens after the early adopter offer?</h3>
      <p>If you join during the early adopter period, you'll lock in $4.99/month for 6 months. After that, your price updates to $14.99/month. The $4.99 offer applies to the first 50 paid users only. If you want to lock in Lifetime ($199 one-time) instead, you can upgrade anytime and only pay the difference.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DISCLAIMER -->
  <section class="disclaimer">
    <p><strong>Disclaimer:</strong> HoldOff is a tool designed to support you. It is not therapy, diagnosis, or a substitute for professional mental health care. If you're struggling with depression, anxiety, suicidal thoughts, or other mental health concerns, please reach out to a licensed professional or crisis line.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2026 HoldOff. Made for people who deserve better.</p>
    <p>
      <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp;
      <a href="/terms">Terms</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp;
      <a href="https://shouldiholdoff.live/contact">Contact</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp;
      <a href="https://shouldiholdoff.live/affiliate">Affiliate Program</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp;
      <a href="https://shouldiholdoff.live/partnerships">Partnership Application</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp;
      <a href="https://shouldiholdoff.live/suggest">Suggest a Feature</a>
    </p>
  </footer>

  <script>
    function handlePricingCTA() {
      // Check if user is logged in by looking for auth token in cookies
      const cookies = document.cookie.split(';').reduce((acc, c) => {
        const [key, val] = c.trim().split('=');
        acc[key] = val;
        return acc;
      }, {});

      if (cookies.auth_token) {
        // User is logged in, go to checkout
        window.location.href = 'https://shouldiholdoff.live/checkout';
      } else {
        // User not logged in, go to signup (which will redirect to checkout after)
        window.location.href = 'https://shouldiholdoff.live/signup';
      }
    }
  </script>
  <script src="/js/floating-companions.js" defer></script>
</body>
</html>
